OL,3,CRishi Sunak criticises 'extremists'
OL,4,Cahead of on-campus antisemitism talks
OL,6,FRishi Sunak has condemned "extremists
OL,7,Fat the National Union of Students
OL,8,F(NUS)" who he says opposed the Union
OL,9,Fof Jewish Students' (UJS) support for
OL,10,F"the principle of a Jewish state".
OL,12,FAhead of a meeting with the UJS and
OL,13,FJewish charity the Community Security
OL,14,FTrust (CST) to "listen and learn from
OL,15,Ftheir experiences" on Thursday, the
OL,16,FPrime Minister warned of "students and
OL,17,Facademic staff being targeted,
OL,18,Fthreatened, and assaulted simply for
OL,19,Fbeing Jewish".
