OL,6,FMr Sunak wrote: "I understand the
OL,7,Fstrength of feeling over recent events
OL,8,Fin Israel and Gaza. No one is saying
OL,9,Fthat students should not be able to
OL,10,Fexpress the very human angst that many
OL,11,Fof us feel about the terrible
OL,12,Fsuffering of war.
OL,14,F"We will always protect freedom of
OL,15,Fspeech and the right to protest ` and
OL,16,Four universities are a natural place
OL,17,Ffor that expression, precisely because
OL,18,Fthey are institutions of learning and
OL,19,Fexploration where challenging ideas
OL,20,Fare debated rigorously.
