OL,3,CRishi Sunak criticises 'extremists'
OL,4,Cahead of on-campus antisemitism talks
OL,6,F"But just as importantly, universities
OL,7,Fhave a profound duty to remain
OL,8,Fbastions of tolerance, where such
OL,9,Fdebate takes place with respect for
OL,10,Fothers ` and where every student feels
OL,11,Fsafe and at home, whatever their faith
OL,12,For background."
OL,14,FMr Sunak's comments come in the wake
OL,15,Fof calls from the Education Secretary,
OL,16,Fwho has said universities must "crack
OL,17,Fdown" on antisemitic abuse on campuses
OL,18,Fand ensure protests do not disrupt
OL,19,Funiversity life.
