OL,6,FMinisters will call on university
OL,7,Fleaders to take immediate disciplinary
OL,8,Faction if any student is found to be
OL,9,Finciting racial hatred or violence and
OL,10,Fto contact the police if a criminal
OL,11,Fact has been committed.
OL,13,FPro-Palestine encampments have been
OL,14,Fset up by students at more than a
OL,15,Fdozen universities across the UK
OL,16,Fagainst the war in Gaza, including
OL,17,FCambridge and Oxford.
