OL,4,Cahead of on-campus antisemitism talks
OL,6,FVice-chancellors from some of the
OL,7,Fleading universities in the UK will
OL,8,Fmeet at Number 10 on Thursday to
OL,9,Fdiscuss action to address the rise in
OL,10,Fantisemitic abuse on campuses and
OL,11,Fdisruption to students' learning.
OL,13,FMr Sunak, Education Secretary Gillian
OL,14,FKeegan, Communities Secretary Michael
OL,15,FGove and Security Minister Tom
OL,16,FTugendhat will call for a zero-
OL,17,Ftolerance approach to antisemitic
OL,18,Fabuse at universities.
