OL,4,Cahead of on-campus antisemitism talks
OL,6,FAhead of the meeting, Ms Keegan said:
OL,7,F"I have made it absolutely clear that
OL,8,Funiversities must crack down on
OL,9,Fantisemitic abuse and ensure that
OL,10,Fprotests do not unduly disrupt
OL,11,Funiversity life."
OL,13,FShe said she hoped it would help
OL,14,Fensure that there are steps in place
OL,15,Fto protect Jewish students.
OL,17,FIn the autumn statement in November,
OL,18,Fthe Chancellor announced that #7
OL,19,Fmillion of extra support would be
OL,20,Fcommitted to tackle antisemitism in
OL,21,Fschools and universities.
