OL,6,FOf this, #500,000 will be dedicated to
OL,7,Fsupporting the work of the University
OL,8,FJewish Chaplaincy, which helps
OL,9,Fstudents deal with incidents of
OL,10,Fantisemitism and intimidation.
OL,12,FThe UJS has criticised encampment
OL,13,Fprotests for creating a "hostile and
OL,14,Ftoxic atmosphere" on campus for Jewish
OL,15,Fstudents.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Edward Isaacs, president
OL,18,Fof the UJS, said "university inaction"
OL,19,Fagainst hateful language from protests
OL,20,F"only serves to alienate Jewish
OL,21,Fstudents from campus".
