OL,6,FIn 2023, 182 university-related
OL,7,Fantisemitic incidents were recorded by
OL,8,Fthe CST compared with 60 incidents in
OL,9,F2022 ` a rise of 203%.
OL,11,FMark Gardner, chief executive of the
OL,12,FCST, said: "The growth of antisemitism
OL,13,Fon British campuses is appalling and
OL,14,Fan affront to the fundamental
OL,15,Fprinciples and values of university
OL,16,Flife.
