OL,6,F"Everyone has the right to protest,
OL,7,Fbut they do not have the right to
OL,8,Fdisrupt other students' learning,
OL,9,Fharass and threaten Jewish students,
OL,10,For spread hatred of Israel with calls
OL,11,Ffor 'resistance' and other extremist
OL,12,Flanguage.
OL,14,F"University authorities need to set
OL,15,Fout clear boundaries for the timing,
OL,16,Flocation and content of these protests
OL,17,Fand ensure there are consequences for
OL,18,Fanyone who breaks them."
