OL,7,F"Government and university leaders
OL,8,Fmust acknowledge the surge in
OL,9,Fantisemitic incidents since October 7,
OL,10,FUJS's increased support efforts, and
OL,11,Fthe resilience of Jewish students.
OL,13,F"Universities must act decisively to
OL,14,Fcombat hate on campus. UJS stands
OL,15,Fready to work with all stakeholders to
